FBIS4-42079 "drweu104_h_94019" FBIS-WEU-94-104 Daily Report 31 May 1994 GERMANY Cooperation With Foreign Arms Firms To Be Easier Cooperation With Foreign Arms Firms To Be Easier LD3105104994 Berlin N-TV in German 1000 GMT 31 May 94 LD3105104994 Berlin N-TV German BFN [Text] German armament companies will be able to cooperate more easily with foreign companies with immediate effect. Joint projects with firms from the 25 OECD countries will be made simpler. Authorization on an individual basis will usually not be necessary. This new provision was decided by the Federal Security Council.
